These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, january
City: miami, prague
House: art-deco, futuristic
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Birthday       | january       | july |
| City         | prague | miami  |
| House       | futuristic    | art-deco    |
| Flower   | amaryllis       | azalea      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, emerald
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, polish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, cain
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, january
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Color      | emerald     | green |
| Nationality           | canadian | polish      |
| Cigar   | cain  | dannemann      |
| Birthday         | february | january     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, chestnut
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid
House: colonial, farmhouse
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Color      | blood-red | chestnut  |
| Game          | whist    | snooker   |
| Flower   | orchid  | lily   |
| House     | farmhouse     | colonial |

