.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: polish, brazilian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, golf
2 different pets are kept: frog, bird
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the polish##1
3. the brazilian is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Nationality      | polish       | brazilian |
| Sport          | golf         | basketball    |
| Pet           | bird | frog    |
| Flower   | iris           | zinnia   |

