2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the project-manager is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job         | doctor | project-manager   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | lemonade       |
| Birthday         | july   | april |
| Cigar     | bluemaster    | vegafina     |

