1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
