.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, september
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, badminton
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | september | december     |
| Cigar   | swisher          | ritmeester |
| Sport           | ice-hockey          | badminton    |
| Beverage     | cola            | coffee       |

 